---
title: '.eco news - latest news about .eco domain names and the .eco community'
description: 'Recent news from the .eco domain registry covering eco-friendly technology and the .eco community.'
page-path: news/
og-image: opengraph/building-og.png
og-width: 1200
og-height: 630
active: news
---

<link rel="preload" as="image" href="/img/glacier-crop.jpeg" />

<div class="jumbotron news-header"
  style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('/img/glacier-crop.jpeg'); background-size: cover">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>.eco news</h1>
    <p>Latest news about .eco domain names, eco-friendly web technology and the .eco community.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="news-headlines container">
  <div class="row g-0">
    {{#each collections.news}}
    <div class="col-md-{{newsColumns @index}}">
      <a href="/{{pagePath path}}">
        <div class="news-tile" style="background-image: url({{ header-img }})">
          <div class="news-tile-overlay">
            <div class="news-tile-content">
              <h3>{{ title }}</h3>
              <p>{{ formatDay pubdate }}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
</section>
